author: BenjaminRS
body: This PR supersedes #24 and adds ontop of #26 the missing LUTs which are currently present in the [L1T offline fork](https://github.com/cms-l1t-offline/L1Trigger-L1TCalorimeter) but not in central cms-data. It adds in the missing 49 files which moves the folder size 57 MB  64 MB (<7 MB).
title: Adding LUTs present in the L1T Offline fork but missing in central
